    <p class="section-intro fade-in">This guide takes you from a blank PowerPoint file to a finished, governed, reusable template (a <code>.potx</code>) that produces beautiful, on-brand slides — whether a person builds the deck or Microsoft&nbsp;365 Copilot generates it. A complete novice can follow along; experienced designers get the precise numbers.</p>
